    66→- effort: TRIVIAL (<5 min), QUICK (5-30 min), STANDARD (30 min - 2 hrs), THOROUGH (2+ hrs)
    67→- is_new_topic: true if this is a distinctly different topic from previous context, false if continuation
    68→
